		"Name": "Fisher King",
		"Details": "Some call him Lucan Marshal. Some call him Syr Wulf. All know his 'Mech, the Fisher King. While the pilot is enigmatic and reserved outside of the arena, inside of it he's a terror, smashing through opponents with Fisher King's mix of high tech and Periphery equipment. In addition to Fisher King's Sword, the heavily modified Excalibur also carries a Medium Cannon (with ammo feed), a RL-20 (again with ammo feed), a MRM-10, and a Snub-Nose PPC to round it out. Fisher King's armor is Periphery-spec Light Plating and the myomer is enhanced with Prototype TSM but the design gets it done in the arenas to a backdrop of a roaring crowd, so clearly Syr Wulf/Lucan Marshal is doing something right.",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_excalibur"
	},
